<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Application Received — TektonX</title>
  <style>
    body { margin: 0; padding: 0; background: #f4f4f5; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; }
    .wrapper { max-width: 560px; margin: 40px auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,.12); }
    .header { background: #0f172a; padding: 32px 40px; text-align: center; }
    .header img { height: 36px; width: auto; display: block; margin: 0 auto; }
    .body { padding: 40px; }
    .body h2 { color: #0f172a; margin-top: 0; font-size: 20px; }
    .body p { color: #475569; line-height: 1.6; margin: 12px 0; }
    .pipeline { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 0; margin: 24px 0; }
    .step { text-align: center; flex: 1; }
    .step .dot { width: 32px; height: 32px; border-radius: 50%; margin: 0 auto 6px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; }
    .step .dot.active { background: #7c3aed; color: #ffffff; }
    .step .dot.inactive { background: #e2e8f0; color: #94a3b8; }
    .step .label { font-size: 11px; color: #94a3b8; font-weight: 500; }
    .step .label.active { color: #7c3aed; font-weight: 700; }
    .connector { height: 2px; flex: 0.5; background: #e2e8f0; margin-bottom: 22px; }
    .badge { display: inline-block; padding: 6px 14px; background: #ede9fe; color: #5b21b6; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; margin: 8px 0; }
    .footer { padding: 20px 40px; background: #f8fafc; text-align: center; }
    .footer p { color: #94a3b8; font-size: 12px; margin: 0; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="header">
      <img src="{{frontendUrl}}/logo-white-horizontal.svg" alt="TektonX" style="height:72px;width:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;" />
    </div>
    <div class="body">
      <h2>Application Received, {{name}}!</h2>
      <span class="badge">Applied</span>
      <div class="pipeline">
        <div class="step">
          <div class="dot active">1</div>
          <div class="label active">Applied</div>
        </div>
        <div class="connector"></div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="dot inactive">2</div>
          <div class="label">Screened</div>
        </div>
        <div class="connector"></div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="dot inactive">3</div>
          <div class="label">Approved</div>
        </div>
        <div class="connector"></div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="dot inactive">4</div>
          <div class="label">Enrolled</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p>Thank you for applying to TektonX! Your application is under review. We'll be in touch with next steps.</p>
      <p>In the meantime, if you have any questions feel free to reach us at <a href="mailto:tektonxlabs@gmail.com" style="color:#7c3aed;">tektonxlabs@gmail.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; {{year}} TektonX Labs. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
